SEARCH
Package com.flipkart.dao

Interface StudentDAOInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
StudentDAOImpl
public interface StudentDAOInterface
Interface representing the data access object (DAO) for student-related operations. Provides methods for managing student accounts, courses, payments, and report cards.
